      <title>AI内存热潮推动SK海力士实现2010年以来最快的销售额增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/sk-hynix-logs-fastest-sales-growth-since-2010-on-ai-memory-boom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SK 海力士公司表示，预计在人工智能相关需求激增的带动下，存储器市场将全面复苏，并取消了资本支出计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/sk-hynix-logs-fastest-sales-growth-since-2010-on-ai-memory-boom</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 23:09:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
